title: Uzhaithu Vaazha Vendum
subTitle: Raja is a poor man who lives with his family that is dependent on him. However, instead of taking up their responsibility, he falls for a wealthy Sandhya and lies to her to win her attention.

title: Teleshopping
subTitle: Learn about a wide selection of products and take advantage of a convenient method of shopping. A show for those who love to shop from the comforts of their home.

title: Indira
subTitle: When one of the leaders from two conflicting villages gets killed, his daughter assumes the leadership and bravely strives to reunite the villages.

title: Kondaan Koduthaan
subTitle: Raasu falls in love with his cousin, Sevandhi, and wants to marry her. However, when Sevandhi's brother, who is betrothed to Raasu's sister, dies suddenly, Raasu and Sevandhi's lives change.

subTitle: Sabhapathy, a footballer, finds his lover dead after returning from his match. Unable to bear the grief, he slips into depression and yearns to become one with her.

title: Kaadhalagi

title: Filler

title: Sakalakala Vallavan
subTitle: Shakti learns that the girl he loves, Anjali, is the cousin of his arch nemesis. Subsequently, his family tries to split them apart by compelling him to wed Divya.
